OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773765948
OL,3,CForce's terrorist response
OL,4,C'inadequate' on night of Nottingham
OL,5,Cattacks inquiry
OL,7,FThe inquiry into the Nottingham
OL,8,Fattacks has heard there was a failure
OL,9,Fin the way that police responded to
OL,10,FValdo Calocane after he killed three
OL,11,Fpeople in June 2023.
OL,13,FThe response policing inspector at the
OL,14,Fscene of the attacks was "completely
OL,15,Fin the dark" that the forces terrorist
OL,16,Fprotocol had been declared until four
OL,17,Fand a half hours after it had been
OL,18,Ftriggered.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773765948
OL,3,CForce's terrorist response
OL,4,C'inadequate' on night of Nottingham
OL,5,Cattacks inquiry
OL,7,FSophie Cartwright KC, who represents
OL,8,Ftwo of the survivors of the attacks,
OL,9,Fasked Inspector Peter Shaw: "You were
OL,10,Fnot made aware when the Plato was
OL,11,Fdeclared shortly after half-past-five
OL,12,Fin the morning, and so that in itself,
OL,13,Fwould you agree, is a systemic failure
OL,14,Fthat happened on the night?"
OL,16,FHe said: "Yes."
OL,26,@qD@]OUvD@\O]xD@JOUxD@OO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773765948
OL,3,CForce's terrorist response
OL,4,C'inadequate' on night of Nottingham
OL,5,Cattacks inquiry
OL,7,FMs Cartwright continued: "And so it
OL,8,Fshows, would you agree, that
OL,9,FNottingham Police on June 13 2023 was
OL,10,Ffundamentally ill-prepared for a
OL,11,Fterrorist attack?"
OL,13,FMr Shaw said: "I can say that I wasn't
OL,14,Ftold, which is a massive deviation
OL,15,Ffrom the plan, yes."
OL,17,FOperation Plato is the national
OL,18,Femergency services protocol for
OL,19,Fresponding to a "marauding terrorist
OL,20,Fattack".
OL,26,@oD@ZOUsD@RO]uD@OOUwD@TO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773765948
OL,3,CForce's terrorist response
OL,4,C'inadequate' on night of Nottingham
OL,5,Cattacks inquiry
OL,7,FIt was engaged after Calocane killed
OL,8,Fstudents Barnaby Webber, Grace
OL,9,FO'Malley Kumar and grandfather Ian
OL,10,FCoates and after he ran over three
OL,11,Fpeople with a van he stole from Ian
OL,12,FCoates.
OL,14,FMr Shaw told the inquiry, which is
OL,15,Fbeing held in central London: "It is a
OL,16,FPlato failure in terms of the ground
OL,17,F(commander) not being informed."
OL,26,@wD@_OUyD@`O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773765948
OL,3,CForce's terrorist response
OL,4,C'inadequate' on night of Nottingham
OL,5,Cattacks inquiry
OL,7,FHe added: "I think to say that the
OL,8,Forganisation was fundamentally ill-
OL,9,Fprepared is a bit of a leap from a
OL,10,Fmistake on that night of me not being
OL,11,Ftold.
OL,13,F"I wouldn't like to stretch that to
OL,14,Fthe whole organisation because there
OL,15,Fare plans, and there are plans to tell
OL,16,Fme, so that was an error on that night
OL,17,Frather than the organisation not being
OL,18,Fprepared.
OL,26,@oD@KOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773765948
OL,3,CForce's terrorist response
OL,4,C'inadequate' on night of Nottingham
OL,5,Cattacks inquiry
OL,7,F"The first I knew was when the daytime
OL,8,F(force incident manager) called me...
OL,9,Fand was surprised that I didn't know
OL,10,Fthat there had been a Plato
OL,11,Fdeclaration."
OL,13,FMs Cartwright asked why it was not
OL,14,Fengaged after officers obtained
OL,15,Ffootage showing the "ferocity" of
OL,16,FCalocane's attack on Mr Webber and Ms
OL,17,FO'Malley-Kumar.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@MO]wD@UOUwD@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773765948
OL,3,CForce's terrorist response
OL,4,C'inadequate' on night of Nottingham
OL,5,Cattacks inquiry
OL,7,FShe said: "Would you agree... that
OL,8,Fthis was a frenzied marauding attack
OL,9,Fthat could have been, even at the
OL,10,Fearly stage, engaging Operation Plato?"
OL,12,FMr Shaw responded: "I wouldn't say
OL,13,Fthat looking at that footage would
OL,14,Fsuggest a marauding attack."
OL,16,FThe inquiry continues.
OL,26,@oD@KOUrD@gO]tD@TOUvD@\O]
